{"tid":2018310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得 黃營嘅人行動力差咗","createTime":"2020-05-15T14:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T00:56:38.000Z","uid":34515,"like":76,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b822c616fe811a8ef396d30afbcbbcf321c5d527","tid":2018310,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個好悶嘅post<br />\n連登應該有幾千個差唔多嘅<br />\n內容都係 睇完今日新聞<br />\n你有咩可以做 叫大家一齊堅持下<br />\n冇乜特別<br />\n但我覺得 連登多一個呢啲post都好過多一個分化post<br />\n所以用咗少少時間打呢幾段嘢<br />\n同揀咗幾張 一路都喺我電話冇Del過嘅相<br />\n<br />\n聯署？Twitter ? Youtube CLS ? 黃色經濟圈？<br />\n都係基本 我就講下有咩基本嘢<br />\n俾你哋諗下自己有咩可以做<br />\n<br />\n聯署<br />\n儲極都唔夠10萬<br />\n奶茶聯盟 三不投<br />\n仲有好多好多嘅白宮聯署...<br />\n其實連登cc台成日都有 只係上唔到熱門<br />\n下次見到就簽 唔好懶好冇？<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 由上年開始<br />\n高峰嗰陣 好多post都有1000至2000 retweet<br />\n宜家呢 得閒先揾到一兩個post上千<br />\n仲要前排少到連Enzo Mazak都發現越嚟越少Twitter手足<br />\n所以 手足們<br />\n一日用多5分鐘上twitter retweet下都唔難啊<br />\n<br />\n講Youtube 雖然佢奶共<br />\n但我哋仲要善用每個平台 俾黃營Youtuber又好<br />\n俾媒體 包括 RTHK 多一個平台都好<br />\n近排好多黃營youtuber views都少咗<br />\n(聽聞藍營youtuber撈得唔錯 小人物都有幾萬)<br />\n希望大家 就算唔特別鐘意睇都好<br />\n得閒開下 較1.5倍速聽youtube<br />\n特別係聽下知識性嘅嘅 比如沈旭暉講政治同歷史<br />\n或者睇多啲唔同嘅範疇<br />\n以我所知有黃營畫室 露營達人 財經 飲食嘅都有<br />\n呢啲更加需要我哋200萬人支持<br />\n一定一定要教屋企黃嘅父母或者老人家睇Youtube 佢哋係最有時間成為黃youtuber嘅忠實支持者<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈 <br />\n唔知大家懲罰黃店到咩程度<br />\n但好想大家堅持<br />\n疫情之後 抗爭會繼續<br />\n經濟差 咩店都難做<br />\n所以可唔可以應承我同你自己<br />\n有得俾黃店賺嘅錢就俾黃店賺<br />\n有得唔撘黨鐵就唔撘黨鐵"},{"pid":"d2065b3e0d517f31a184b26aab8121521aecc3e9","tid":2018310,"uid":264326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"此告急文宣絕對係廣告，自費架屌你！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2018306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2018306</a>"},{"pid":"2b8fcbce30eae4561c20f31466e02191245efd32","tid":2018310,"uid":34515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:03:44.000Z","msg":"希望疫情之後<br />\n大家唔好淨係掛住吃喝玩樂 (好擔心)<br />\n知大家辛苦 已經好幾個月fd又冇得約<br />\n街又冇得出<br />\n但唔係話要痛苦修行<br />\n而係學下將抗爭融入生活<br />\n<br />\n睇完今日新聞 係咪覺得世界好黑暗<br />\n覺得好攰 無力感係俾過往幾個月更大<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係望下今日係咩日子 其實我哋唔孤單<br />\n我哋仲有獄中手足 天上面嘅手足 海外流亡嘅手足</span>"},{"pid":"c62ba22f5ab6634a1dd9be783246591462f544ab","tid":2018310,"uid":34515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WeEYARy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWeEYARy.jpg&h=3154105c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7iLEkif.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iLEkif.jpg&h=4ff6a482&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbvtdDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxbvtdDg.jpg&h=e6f72c78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GZNubE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GZNubE.png&h=0b5d4b69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JwsubG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JwsubG.jpg&h=f7c73cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9joiARH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9joiARH.jpg&h=c26934a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kKarYn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kKarYn.jpg&h=b3da3ee0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6feeda1b7c3d0edbcef8ab562e37018644eb65dd","tid":2018310,"uid":15125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:14:08.000Z","msg":"冇 完"},{"pid":"894ff19179ed197a8b5d562f01fbd05b41768822","tid":2018310,"uid":10540,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"黃營唔少都準備移民中"},{"pid":"66a60f3b6bae31e78d6fcbd3e8baee83b8b556e9","tid":2018310,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b822c616fe811a8ef396d30afbcbbcf321c5d527","tid":2018310,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0